一个方便、一致的模板，主要用于在参考文献中标示一个或多个页码，并在数字之前提供了[[不换行空格]]。
<!--A convenience{{\}}consistency template, primarily intended for use when citing a page number or range of pages as part of a reference, that incorporates a [[non-breaking space]] (&amp;nbsp;) before the number/s supplied.-->

== 样例 ==
{{Aligned table
 |col1style=padding-right:2.0em;
